
Prerequisites:

cmake, opencv


To compile in the lab
——————————

run ./lab_config.sh
cd build
make

To compile on your own machine
———

cd build/
cmake ../
make


To run
——

In the build folder:
./sc image1 new_width new_height image2


References
——
1. https://docs.opencv.org/2.4.13.7/doc/tutorials/imgproc/imgtrans/sobel_derivatives/sobel_derivatives.html
2. https://people.revoledu.com/kardi/tutorial/Similarity/EuclideanDistance.html
3. https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/minimum-cut-in-a-directed-graph/ 

